Trade/Device Name(s): Carolina Liquid Chemistries CLC 6410 Chemistry Analyzer
Carolina Liquid Chemistries ISE Calibrator Kit
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Carolina Liquid Chemistries CLC 6410 Chemistry Analyzer
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Carolina Liquid Chemistries CLC 6410 Chemistry Analyzer, Glucose Reagent, ISE Kit, and ISE Calibrator Kit for quantitative determination of glucose and electrolytes in serum and plasma.
Indications for Use Summary: Automated analyzer and associated reagents and calibrators for quantitative in vitro measurement of glucose, sodium, potassium, and chloride in serum and plasma for diagnosis and management of carbohydrate metabolism and electrolyte disorders.
